quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  37,114,GomЙ—ii Men moЖґЖґike e dow Muusaa e Haaruuna
  37,115,"Men daЙ—ni Й“e, kamЙ“e e yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, e ngoЖґo mawnungo"
  37,116,"Men walli Й“e, Й“e woni fooluЙ“e Й“en"
  37,117,Men okki Й“e Deftere Й“annginnde nden
  37,118,"Men fewniri Й“e, e laawol focciingol ngol"
  37,119,"Men accani Й“e mantoore, e sakkitiiЙ“e Й“en"
  37,120,Kisal wonii e dow Muusaa e Haaruuna
  37,121,Ko wano nii Men yoЙ“itirta moЖґЖґimЙ“e Й“en
  37,122,"KamЙ“e Й—iЙ—o, ko Й“e jeyanooЙ“e e jeyaaЙ“e Amen gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  37,123,"Pellet, Ilyaasa kadi, ko jeyanooЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  37,124,"Janto nde o maakannoo yimЙ“e makko Й“en: \"E on hulataa [Alla]"
  37,125,"E ko \"Ba'ala\" rewoton, accon Й“urЙ—o moЖґЖґude tagu On"
  37,126,"Woni Alla, JeyЙ—o on, Jeyi baabiraaЙ“e mon adinooЙ“e Й“en"
  37,127,"ЖЃe fenni mo, awa non, ko Й“e tawnoyteeЙ“e (ka lepte)"
  37,128,Si wanaa jeyaaЙ“e Alla laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“en
  37,129,"Men accani mo mantoore, e sakkitiiЙ“e Й“en"
  37,130,Kisal wonii e dow Ilyaasiina'en
  37,131,Ko wano nii Men yoЙ“irta moЖґЖґimЙ“e Й“en
  37,132,"Kanko, ko o jeyanooЙ—o e jeyaaЙ“e Amen gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  37,133,"Pellet, Luutu kadi, ko jeyanooЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Й“en"
  37,134,"Janto nde Men daЙ—ndunoo mo, kanko e Й“eynguure makko nden fow"
  37,135,"si wonaa nayeeja debba, tawaaЙ—o e luttunooЙ“e Й“en"
  37,136,refti Men oЖґЖґi heddii Й“e Й“en
  37,137,"Onon non, hiЙ—on rewa e hoore-maЙ“Й“e, dawol mon"
  37,138,e ka jemma. E on haqqiltaa